<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Stockify</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f8fafc; border-radius: 5px;">
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px;">
                <h1 style="color: #2563eb; text-align: center;">Welcome to Stockify!</h1>
                <p style="font-size: 16px;">Dear <%= @email %>,</p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px;">Thank you for registering with Stockify. We're excited to have you on board!</p>
                <div style="background-color: #fff; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;">
                    <h2 style="color: #2563eb; margin-top: 0;">Confirm Your Account</h2>
                    <p style="font-size: 16px;">Please confirm your account email by clicking the link below:</p>
                    <p style="text-align: center;">
                        <a href="<%= confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #2563eb; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;">Confirm my account</a>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <h3 style="color: #2563eb;">What's Next?</h3>
                <ol style="font-size: 16px;">
                    <li>Click the confirmation link above to verify your email.</li>
                    <li>Our admin team will review your registration details.</li>
                    <li>You'll receive another email once your account is approved.</li>
                    <li>After approval, you can log in and start trading!</li>
                </ol>
                <p style="font-size: 16px;">The approval process typically takes 1-2 business days after email confirmation. We appreciate your patience during this time.</p>
                <div style="background-color: #fef3c7; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
                    <h3 style="color: #92400e; margin-top: 0;">Important Note</h3>
                    <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #92400e;">Please confirm your email and wait for the account approval email before attempting to log in. If you have any questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
                </div>
                <p style="font-size: 16px;">If you need any assistance or have any questions, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@stockify.com" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;">support@stockify.com</a>.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 16px;">Best regards,<br>The Stockify Pro Team</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
</body>
</html>